  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were awakened up in the middle of the night because she was unconscious.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I, I got up also and learned what was happening with her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I wanted-- that, that year, particularly in this fifth class of gymnasium, there we had it in our-- in the book, first aid.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I read what is the first aid, what to do under such circumstances.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I ran into that house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And all I had to do is to open a window and put her head in hot water.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That's what they gave as a-- as a remedy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And sure enough, she opened her eyes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so the next day, it was like I saved her life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I'm not-- I cannot say that I really saved her life, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But, but that at any rate, that was necessary to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I read at that time a book-- a book which was written by [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And it was called, which means 'homeless people.' And the book is about a doctor [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who worked [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in, in, in poverty circles-- in, in the book.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] serving people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that was-- appealed to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So whether it's a book, or whether it's the admiration, that I, all of a sudden, in the-- in the eyes of that neighbor, I was somebody, like, saving her.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Or whether it was, because whenever somebody was sick in that shtetl, they used to call my mother to, to take care of them, to help take care-- and she liked to do it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "This I'm adding now, after years, that maybe that was my mother's contribution to it also.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
